tr.ti:
Path to the ebuild's files/ directory, commonly used
for small patches and files. For example:
"${PORTDIR}/${CATEGORY}/${PN}/files".

ul.li:
using ${PV} and the variables derived from it (${P},
${MY_P}…) in SRC_URI and S to avoid having
to update those variables for every version bump (assuming that
${PV} is used to indicate the upstream version);
